<template>
  <component-render v-slot="props">
    {{ props.desc }}
    <Textbox v-bind="{ ...myProps, ...props.desc }" />
  </component-render>
</template>
<script>

import { Textbox } from '@phila/phila-ui';
import ComponentRender from '@/components/examples/ComponentRender';

export default {
  components: {
    Textbox,
    ComponentRender,
  },
  data () {
    return {
      myProps: {
        desc: "nope",
      },
    };
  },
};
</script>
